#Write a Python function that solves the problem: "Bethany can run 10 laps on the track in one hour.  Trey can run 4 more laps than Bethany.  Shaelyn can run half as many laps as Trey.  Quinn can run 2 fewer laps than Shaelyn.  How many more laps can Bethany run compared to Quinn?"
def solve_laps(b, t, s, q, total_laps):
    return total_laps - ((b * t) + (t - s) + (s / q))
